Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:31.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,Nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:35.27,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Do you know the rumor about the tunnel that can give you anything you want?}Cậu biết lời đồn về đường hầm sẽ cho cậu mọi thứ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:36.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,{What's that?}Là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:39.52,Italics,,0,0,0,,{If you go down that tunnel,}Nếu cậu đi vào đường hầm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.44,Italics,,0,0,0,,{your wish will come true.}Điều ước sẽ thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:45.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,{But in exchange, you will age 100 years.}Nhưng đổi lại, sẽ mất 100 năm tuổi thọ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Woah!}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,{What's the name of that tunnel?}Tên đường hầm đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:50.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,{The name of the tunnel is...}Tên của nó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{...Urashima Tunnel.}Đường hầm Urashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{I think I need more money.}Cần tiền ghê đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to buy something.}Tớ muốn mua vài thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you're in remote areas like this, your money is rarely used.}Ở miền quê này thì xài tiền mấy đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes, yes.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{After graduation I want to go to Tokyo.}Sau khi tốt nghiệp tớ sẽ lên Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.69,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Currently, the Oosara to Sugimori trains,}Tuyến Oosara đến Sugimori,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:32.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,{had an accidents due to animal collisions.}hiện tại đang dừng do có tai nạn với thú hoang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:38.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Due to that, the next train will come about 30 minutes later.}Tàu sẽ đến trễn 30 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,{We apologize for the inconvenience.}Chúng tôi vô cùng xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.62,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Please wait a moment.}Xin hãy chờ một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{Seeing people with strange looks is disgust, you know.}Nhìn chằm chằm vào người khác tởm lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{You don't look like you're used to being here.}Trông cậu không phải người ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{The train is late because of the deer, it's common here.}Tàu tông trúng hươu nai là chuyện thường ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is my umbrella.}Đây là dù của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{Want to use?}Muốn dùng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ý gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because you don't have an umbrella,}Thì cậu không có dù.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm afraid your bag will get wet too.}Túi của cậu sẽ ướt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{Guess what? Want to look good?}Gì thế? Ra vẻ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{If I borrow it, then what will you use?}Nếu tôi mượn thì cậu về bằng gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Do you have a spare umbrella?}Cậu có cây khác à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nothing, but my house is close to the station.}Không, nhưng nhà tôi gần ga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's not an answer.}Trả lời chẳng khớp gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you have the flu,}Nếu cậu bị cảm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{your parents will worry, you know.}ba mẹ cậu sẽ lo lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's exactly you too, right?}Thế cậu thì không à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{No one worries about me at home.}Không ai lo cho tôi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't have parents.}Tôi không có ba mẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's good.}Tuyệt nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can I borrow your umbrella?}Tôi mượn dù nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can you tell me your name and phone number?}Tên cậu và số điện thoại?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{I must return what I borrowed.}Mượn đồ thì phải trả.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll contact you later.}Tôi sẽ liên lạc sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Touno Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, calm down.}Mọi người trật tự.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Lesson will start soon.}Chuẩn bị vào tiết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{And also, today I want to introduce a new student.}Và hôm nay cô sẽ giới thiệu học sinh mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.18,Top,,0,0,0,,{You see? There's a new student.}Có học sinh chuyển trường à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{He moved from Tokyo, his name is Hanashiro Anzu.}Em ấy chuyển đến từ Tokyo, Hanashiro Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, Hanashiro-san, please introduce yourself...}Hanashiro, giới thiệu đi em...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nothing special.}Không có gì đặc biệt cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can I sit now?}Em xuống chỗ ngồi nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay.}À ừ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{We are classmates, huh?}Chúng ta học cùng lớp à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{So don't bother looking for contacts.}Có vẻ xin số điện thoại hơi thừa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll return your umbrella tomorrow, OK?}Tôi sẽ trả dù cho cậu vào ngày mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{What? What umbrella?}Hả? Dù gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are they both acquaintances?}Người quen à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.13,Top,,0,0,0,,{Did something happen?}Có chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{After the break, let's chat with him, shall we?}Lát nữa nghỉ trưa lại bắt chuyện xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{All right, now, the lesson is about to begin.}Nào, chuẩn bị bài học thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, where do you live?}Nè, cậu sống ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Do you have any hobbies?}Có sở thích nào không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Does it have anything to do with you guys?}Liên quan gì tới mấy người?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro-san, what are you reading?}Hanashiro, cậu đọc gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{After school, let's go to the cafe near the station, shall we?}Sau giờ học, đi uống nước không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please don't talk to me.}Đừng bắt chuyện với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro-san, where do you want to have lunch?}Hanashiro, cậu ăn trưa ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's eat together, shall we?}Ăn cùng nhau đi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm done eating.}Tôi ăn xong rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{What an arrogant.}Đỉnh thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{His demeanor was cold.}Lạnh lùng ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{He looks flashy.}Nhưng vậy lại gây nổi bật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Soon she will be Kawasaki's target.}Rồi sẽ bị Kawasaki nhắm vào thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Since then, who do you think you are?}Cậu nghĩ mình là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{See.}Đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Only the first day is already very arrogant.}Mới ngày đầu đã ra vẻ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you some princess, huh?}Cậu là công chúa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's this? Manga?}Gì thế? Manga à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{an old one.}Lại còn cũ rích.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can you return it?}Trả đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{I thought you read a serious book.}Cứ tưởng đọc gì ghê gớm lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Give it back.}Trả đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, my hands are slippery.}Xin lỗi, trượt tay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe because the manga is old, to the point where it grows mushrooms.}Chắc tại cũ quá nên mọc rêu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nhớp nháp thấy ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{And you touched it.}Nó chạm vào kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{You guys...}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{...are you looking for trouble?}...mấy người thích gây sự phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{So what?}Thế thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait, the blood is coming out.}Chảy máu kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{Woah! Quickly call the teacher!}Mau gọi giáo viên!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{I will help to!}Tớ đi gọi nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{Talking like that!}Mẹ nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is that damn woman kidding me, huh?}Đừng có đùa với tao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Con ở đó à.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why are you there?}Sao lại xuống đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lấy ít nước.{I'm going to get some water.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Today, that damn woman came to the office.}Hôm nay bà già chết tiệt đó đã đến văn phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's Karen-chan's death day soon, right?}Sắp đến ngày giỗ của Karen-chan rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{He said he wanted to clean up Karen's grave. Your ass!}Bà ta muốn dọn dẹp mộ phần của Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{As if she was a good person, you damn woman.}Tỏ ra là người tốt à? Bà già chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{You think so too, right?}Con cũng nghĩ thế nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vâng cái quái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?}Mày nói gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's all your fault!}Tất cả là tại mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{You killed Karen!}Mày đã giết Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{All you only do is listening music using this!}Mày lúc nào cũng cắm đầu nghe nhạc!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please bring back Karen!}Trả Karen lại đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm ready to give your life in exchange!}Tao sẵn sàng đổi mạng mày lấy con bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Quickly bring Karen to this house!}Nhanh đưa Karen về đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where are you going?}Con đi đâu vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ouch.}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{What place is this?}Nơi nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why this is here...}Tại sao lại ở đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Karen is already...}Karen đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ouch.}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Bird?}Chim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is he alive?}Nó còn sống?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:33.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,{I can hear frogs...}Tôi nghe thấy tiếng ếch ộp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,{...from afar.}...từ phía xa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is this... Kii?}Mày là... Kii?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{He should be dead.}Đáng ra nó phải chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Urashima Tunnel.}Đường hầm Urashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{So it's real?}Nó có thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Impossible...}Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{That song...}Bài hát đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{A song I and Karen wrote for Kii.}Là bài hát mình và Karen đã viết cho Kii.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you Kii, for real?}Là mày thật à, Kii?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Who? Is anyone there?}Ai? Ai ở đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm grateful.}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm afraid that you will disappear.}Ba tưởng con biến mất rồi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{I am sorry.}Con xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{At that time, I was just drunk.}Lúc đó ba hơi say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{So please don't run away again.}Nên đừng bỏ đi nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{I got confused because there was a call from school.}Nhà trường gọi hoài phiền phức lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where are you staying?}Con đã ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're not going to town, are you?}Con không rời khỏi thị trấn này nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, I'm not staying overnight.}Không, con không...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm just taking a walk.}Chỉ đi dạo chút thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay. It's okay if you don't want to say it.}Vậy à. Không muốn nói cũng không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{But, if you run away again for a week, I won't forgive you.}Nhưng lần sau còn bỏ đi cả tuần\N nữa thì ba không tha cho đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{A week?}Cả tuần?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{June 22?}Tháng 6 ngày 22?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you come in for a week?}Tại sao mày lại nghỉ cả tuần thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{I caught the flu out of season.}Thì bị cảm cúm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{So you can't be reached for a week?}Rồi không thèm liên lạc luôn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{I forgot to charge my phone.}Tao quên sạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Fool.}Thằng ngốc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Today you come, huh.}Hôm nay cậu đi học à.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm healthy, really.}Ừm, khoẻ lại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just don't die.}Đừng chết đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you coming in tomorrow?}Mai có đi học không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Usually.}Chắc có.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{All right, I brought your umbrella, OK?}Ừm, vậy mai tôi trả dù.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm sick of seeing it.}Giữ hoài phiền lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{She's worried about you.}Cậu ấy lo cho mày đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Who?}Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Of course you.}Mày chứ ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is not a dream.}Không phải mơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is the real Urashima Tunnel.}Đây là hầm Urashima thực sự.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{If I could bring Karen back...}Nếu có thể mang Karen về...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's this?}Gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro-san?}Hanashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun, where is this?}Touno, đây là đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hurry out!}Mau ra khỏi đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait.}Khoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Actually... what happened?}Chuyện gì... vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can you explain?}Cậu có thể giải thích không?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I see.}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{So this is a tunnel where time runs differently inside and outside, huh?}Đây là đường hầm có dòng thời \Ngian khác với bên ngoài à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{All we go in is only a few seconds.}Chúng ta chỉ vào có vài giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{But outside, it's been five hours.}Nhưng bên ngoài đã 5 tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{So,}Vậy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{if we go inside, we can quickly age.}nếu vào trong lâu, chúng ta sẽ già đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{But in return, we can ask anything.}Nhưng đổi lại... có thể lấy được mọi thứ mình muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, have you got a wish?}Cậu đã lấy được thứ mình muốn chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{But I'm sure.}Nhưng tớ chắc chắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{About this tunnel,}Về cái đường hầm này.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{have you told other people?}Cậu có nói cho ai chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sao mà nói được.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{No one believes that it's just a rumour, right?}Có nói cũng chả ai tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{We have to try it ourselves.}Chúng ta phải thử nghiệm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun.}Touno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Would you like to join me?}Cậu muốn tham gia với tôi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.61,0:22:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{I also have a wish.}Tôi cũng có thứ mình muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{You must have a wish too.}Và cậu cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{If our goals are the same,}Nếu chúng ta có cùng mục đích,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.95,0:22:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{and walk through this tunnel together,}vậy cả hai cùng nhau đi vào đường hầm,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{this will be easier, right?}thì mọi chuyện sẽ dễ dàng hơn, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{I do it for myself,}Tôi làm nó vì bản thân,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{you also do it for yourself.}cậu cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{How?}Thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{This isn't a bad thing, is it?}Không phải thoả thuận tồi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{Greetings again.}Mong cậu giúp đỡ lần nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno Kaoru-kun.}Touno Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Starting today, we will investigate it.}Từ hôm nay chúng ta sẽ cùng điều tra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're ready, right?}Cậu đã sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because at first I did it myself...}Ngay từ đầu tớ đã sẵn sàng...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{...it might be better if you...}quan trọng là cậu cơ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay then.}Vậy thì tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{After school, we'll meet at that railroad crossing.}Sau giờ học gặp nhau ở đoạn giao đường ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{And about the tunnel...}Về đường hầm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{...don't tell anyone else.}đừng nói ai đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's a secret between the two of us.}Là bí mật giữa hai ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, what are we going to do with it?}Thế giờ làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{First, let's see how different the time is inside and outside the tunnel.}Đầu tiên xác nhận coi thời gian\N bên trong và ngoài cách nhau bao xa?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{As accurate as possible.}Càng chính xác càng tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{How to?}Bằng cách nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:02.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,Cậu có nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{All right, here you go.}Rồi, đi đi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't be silent, OK?}Đừng im lặng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:10.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Keep talking to me, okay?}Nhớ liên tục nói chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:12.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,{If the signal drops...}Nếu mất tín hiệu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.02,Italics,,0,0,0,,{...certainly it was an inflection point in time.}...thì đó chính là vị trí lệch thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.02,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{When it comes to talking...}Nói chuyện liên tục...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:18.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Just small talk.}Thì tìm đại gì đó nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:19.31,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Yes, whatever.}Nói gì cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{Have you ever hit anyone at school before?}Cậu đã từng đánh ai ở trường bao giờ chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.57,0:24:24.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Why suddenly?}Sao tự nhiên?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{You said whatever.}Thì cậu kêu nói gì cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.82,0:24:27.78,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Nothing, really.}Chưa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.78,0:24:29.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Except Kawasaki-san.}Trừ Kawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.49,0:24:31.53,Italics,,0,0,0,,{She was the first person I punch.}Cậu ta là người đầu tiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.99,0:24:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{You know it's wrong, why don't you apologize to her?}Cậu biết là sai sao không xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.33,0:24:37.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,{The one who's looking for trouble first who should apologize, right?}Kẻ nào gây sự trước phải xin lỗi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.71,0:24:39.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,{And then I apologize after that.}Sau đó tớ sẽ xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.08,0:24:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.96,0:24:43.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,{After all, if she feel insulted...}Với cả nếu cậu ta bị xúc phạm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.00,0:24:44.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,{...obviously she're angry...}thì cũng sẽ tức giận...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.80,0:24:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{It cut off!}Mất sóng rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.09,0:24:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{The phone call disconnected for 65 minutes.}Từ khi mất sóng tới lúc đi ra là 65 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.30,0:24:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though we've only talked for a while,}Chỉ mới nói có vài câu,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:24:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{it's been more than an hour?}mà đã hơn 1 tiếng sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.43,0:24:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, where did the phone cut off?}Thế mất sóng ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.27,0:25:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{When passing momiji pillar.}Khi bước qua mấy cây lá đỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{As expected, this isn't easy.}Quả nhiên, đúng như dự đoán.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.15,0:25:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Alright, let's keep investigating.}Tiếp tục thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.95,0:25:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{To have this tunnel fulfill our wishes.}Để có thể thực hiện mong ước của chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.93,0:25:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Make sure you come back from the momiji pillar within 3 seconds.}Nhớ là phải quay ngược lại trong vòng 3 giây thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.97,0:25:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{3 seconds equals 2 hours.}3 giây là 2 tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.02,0:25:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{That means, 30 seconds equals 20 hours.}Tức là 30 giây sẽ là 20 tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.69,0:25:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{1 hour equals 100 days.}1 tiếng cỡ 100 ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.11,0:25:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{1 day equals 6 and a half years.}1 ngày sẽ bằng 6 năm rưỡi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'd like to see if we can communicate between the inside and outside of the tunnel.}Tớ muốn xem thử có thể nói chuyện \Ngiữa bên trong và ngoài không?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.91,0:25:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuy điện thoại không thể,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.41,0:26:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{we try to use Message.}nhưng thử nhắn tin xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.21,0:26:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is it delivered?}Nó có gửi tới không?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.51,0:26:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just in.}Có.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.93,0:26:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{It seems the time difference is still the same.}Có vẻ thời gian cũng bị lệch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.44,0:26:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Since it's a tunnel, there must be an exit somewhere.}Vì là đường hầm nên phải có lối ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.74,0:26:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Watch out!}Cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.46,0:26:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can you step aside?}Cậu có thể lùi ra chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.45,0:26:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, sorry.}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.23,0:27:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{You've been hanging out with Hanashiro a lot lately, huh?}Gần đây chú mày đi với Hanashiro suốt nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.11,0:27:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just a coincidence.}Tình cờ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.94,0:27:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{You guys are dating?}Hẹn hò à?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.82,0:27:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{Absolutely no!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.53,0:27:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is this really that dead bird?}Đây là con chim đã chết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.53,0:27:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{He can sang my old song.}Nó hót bài hát cũ mà tớ từng dạy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.70,0:27:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm so sure.}Chắc chắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.53,0:27:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{So this makes you even more sure, huh?}Nó khiến cậu khẳng định luôn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.91,0:27:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Did you really take her home?}Mày dẫn em ấy về nhà à?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.21,0:27:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's no deep meaning.}Bình thường mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.17,0:27:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's really deep!}Bình thường cái đầu mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.33,0:27:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Deep as the Mariana Trench!}Mối quan hệ mờ ám!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.92,0:27:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's obvious you two are dating!}Chắc chắn tụi mày đang hẹn hò!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.25,0:27:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{I say no, really!}Không có!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.55,0:27:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{That tunnel...}Đường hầm đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.84,0:27:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{...may have something to do with the town's native customs or beliefs.}...có thể liên quan đến nghi thức \Ncổ xưa nào của thị trấn này.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.18,0:27:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Need we find out?}Tìm hiểu thử không?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.31,0:28:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can we texting from here inside the tunnel?}Chúng ta có thể gửi tin nhắn vào trong không?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.94,0:28:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{We haven't tried it, have we?}Vẫn chưa thử nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.02,0:28:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you can send it from outside to inside, it should also be possible if it's inside here.}Nếu có thể gửi từ trong ra thì ngược lại cũng được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.52,0:28:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{While passing the pillar, I'll try to send you message,}Trong khi vượt qua cây lá phong, tớ sẽ thử gửi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.74,0:28:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{if it's reach you, comes back here again, okay.}Nếu nhận được thì quay lại ngay nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.07,0:28:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.84,0:28:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro-san...}Hanashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.18,0:29:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you okay?}Cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.11,0:29:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{Seven hours.}7 tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.11,0:29:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're slow, huh.}Cậu chậm quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.07,0:29:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{For you, maybe just 10 seconds.}Với cậu có thể chỉ là 10 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.11,0:29:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.99,0:29:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{You didn't do anything bad, right?}Cậu có làm gì sai đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.91,0:29:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{No need to apologize.}Không cần xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.74,0:29:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{How is the message?}Thế tin nhắn thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.54,0:29:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look's like cannot receive message from outside?}Có vẻ không thể nhận tin nhắn từ bên ngoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.38,0:29:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes, I think so to.}Tớ cũng cảm thấy vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.63,0:29:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.26,0:29:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Besides, I never said you could call me by my first name.}Với cả chưa ai cho phép cậu gọi bằng tên cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.55,0:29:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, I let it slip.}Bỏ qua đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.64,0:29:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't mind.}Cơ mà cũng không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.98,0:29:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is it true?}Thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.23,0:29:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's go home, it's late.}Thôi, về nhà đi. Trễ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.64,0:30:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just back and forth 108 seconds,}Chỉ có 108 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.68,0:30:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{equal to 3 days of vacation here, huh.}Mà đã tương đương 3 ngày à...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.83,0:30:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, let's hurry up!}Này, nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.92,0:30:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up!}Nhanh lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.54,0:30:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun, am I late?}Touno, cậu chờ lâu chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.01,0:31:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, you came just in time, really.}Không, cậu đến đúng giờ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.47,0:31:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Punctuality is a natural thing.}Đúng giờ là bình thường mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.22,0:31:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Lets go.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.73,0:31:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why did you take me to the aquarium?}Sao lại mời tớ đi thuỷ cung?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.19,0:31:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because it's the only famous place nearby.}Vì gần đây chỉ có nơi này là nổi tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.86,0:31:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.11,0:31:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Với cả tớ cũng tò mò về cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.36,0:31:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Do not take it wrong.}Đừng tưởng bở.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.03,0:31:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not "like" as such.}Không phải kiểu thích gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.74,0:31:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.33,0:31:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun, I've never seen you laugh before, have I.}Tớ chưa từng thấy cậu cười bao giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.25,0:31:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is it true?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.29,0:31:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.13,0:31:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're confident.}Cậu thì lại quá tự cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.67,0:31:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{And also easy to laugh, yes.}Và cũng dễ cười nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.13,0:31:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is it true?}Thế á?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.34,0:31:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.89,0:31:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{At that time...}Lúc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.50,0:31:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{...as you pass through the pillar.}...khi cậu vượt qua cây cột...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.69,0:32:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm scared.}Tớ đã rất sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.65,0:32:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{They say this tunnel could sever the world.}Họ nói đường hầm đó là nơi đoạn tuyệt với thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.41,0:32:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{Either way, I'm having a hard time getting information.}Tớ cảm thấy không thể nói chuyện được với cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.33,0:32:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, I want to speak to you nicely,}Thế nên tớ muốn giao tiếp nhiều hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.79,0:32:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{as comrades in arms.}Như những người cùng chí hướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.00,0:32:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you're scared, we're done with it.}Nếu sợ thì thôi dừng lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{I won't stop.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.42,0:32:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to get what I want.}Tớ có thứ mình muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.59,0:32:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe during the next investigation, I'll get it.}Có thể lần tới tớ sẽ có được nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.72,0:32:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{You also have a desire like that, right?}Cậu cũng thế mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{In the past, I've come to this aquarium.}Ngày xưa tớ từng đến nơi này rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.82,0:32:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{With father and mother.}Cùng ba mẹ...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.16,0:32:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{And my sister, Karen.}Và em gái Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.87,0:32:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, you have a sister.}Cậu có em gái à.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.12,0:32:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Con bé đã luôn quan tâm tới ba mẹ và tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.54,0:32:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Then?}Đã?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.54,0:33:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{He died, falling from a tree.}Con bé mất do té từ trên cây.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.17,0:33:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{He always thinks about everyone's happiness.}Nó lúc nào cũng nghĩ cho người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.26,0:33:12.09,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{Do you have any wish?}Anh có điều ước gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.39,0:33:13.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{Rhinoceros beetle.}Bắt được bọ cánh cứng.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.35,0:33:14.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{That's easy.}Đơn giản vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.39,0:33:18.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{For I... want a world where everyone laughs.}Còn em... muốn mọi người trên thế giới đều vui vẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.19,0:33:22.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{It's weird to keep laughing.}Ai cũng cười thành ra bị khùng hết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.60,0:33:22.48,Top,,0,0,0,,{He wants a world where everyone is happy.}Con bé muốn mọi người đều hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.44,0:33:24.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{Why? It's a beautiful world, though.}Có sao đâu, thế giới sẽ trở nên vui vẻ mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.61,0:33:27.44,Top,,0,0,0,,{But, on that day I had a fight with Karen over something trivial.}Nhưng vào ngày đó, tớ đã cãi nhau với con bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.78,0:33:29.36,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{I hate you Onii-chan!}Em ghét anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.57,0:33:30.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{I hate you too, really.}Anh cũng ghét em.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:31.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Thế nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.49,0:33:34.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{Lies, I like you Onii-chan, really.}Em xạo thôi, em thương anh lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.24,0:33:35.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{Be careful!}Anh đi cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.66,0:33:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{When I came back, she fell from a tree, and died.}Khi tớ về, con bé đã té từ trên cây và mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.58,0:33:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{She fell while trying to pick up a rhinoceros beetle for me.}Nó muốn bắt bọ cánh cứng cho tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.88,0:33:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{After that, mother left the house.}Sau đó, mẹ tớ rời khỏi nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.21,0:33:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{My father was drunk and scolded me.}Ba thì suốt ngày say xỉn và mắng chửi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.38,0:33:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{My family is so broken.}Gia đình tớ đã tan vỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.14,0:33:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{So what do you want, Touno-kun?}Vậy thứ cậu muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.14,0:34:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to...}Tớ muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.15,0:34:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{...to bring Karen back.}...mang Karen quay lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.95,0:34:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Do I look scary in that tunnel?}Trông tớ... có sợ hãi đường hầm đó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.38,0:34:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Absolutely not.}Hoàn toàn không.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.44,0:34:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{What did you say to your parents?}Cậu nói gì với ba mẹ?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.35,0:34:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Didn't I tell you?}Tớ chưa nói à?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.15,0:34:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't have parents.}Tớ không có ba mẹ.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.28,0:34:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh yes.}À phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.61,0:34:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you ready?}Sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.74,0:34:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.57,0:34:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{We'll be gone and back in 108 seconds.}Chúng ta sẽ quay lại sau 108 giây.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.41,0:34:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{That way, we can come back at the third day of vacation outside.}Tức là vào ngày cuối cùng của kì nghỉ lễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:34:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't fall, OK?}Đừng té đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.24,0:35:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even like this I am pretty good at sports.}Trông thế chứ tớ giỏi thể thao lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.50,0:35:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{We run when I say start.}Chúng ta sẽ chạy khi tớ bắt đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.00,0:35:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ready?}Sẵn sàng...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.92,0:35:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Start!}Bắt đầu!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.44,0:35:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's time, Hanashiro.}Hết giờ rồi, Hanashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.61,0:35:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's come back.}Quay về thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.32,0:35:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.91,0:35:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro, stand up.}Hanashiro, đứng lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.82,0:35:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{We must hurry back.}Chúng ta phải quay lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.83,0:35:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{You go first!}Cậu về trước đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.08,0:35:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll catch up later after picking this.}Tớ sẽ quay ra sau khi lấy chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.83,0:35:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{You cannot.}Không được!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.87,0:35:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just leave that...}Bỏ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.33,0:35:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't leave this!}Không thể!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.30,0:35:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's already everything!}Tất cả rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.66,0:36:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is that what you want?}Đây là thứ cậu muốn?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.58,0:36:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's the only thing that connected me and my grandfather.}Nó là thứ liên kết tớ với ông nội.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.44,0:36:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's already 4 am.}Đã 4 giờ sáng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.40,0:36:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't know what my dad will say if I come home now.}Ba tớ sẽ nói gì khi tớ về giờ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.94,0:36:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{And my clothes are wet too.}Quần áo cũng ướt nhẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.57,0:36:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{In that case,}Nếu vậy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.74,0:37:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Want to come to my house?}muốn ghé nhà tớ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.12,0:37:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Put it on.}Mặc vào đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.75,0:37:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is your father's?}Của ba cậu hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.21,0:37:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{This room used to be occupied by my uncle.}Căn phòng này từng là của chú tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.13,0:37:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{He went back to his hometown, so I stayed here.}Ông ấy về quê rồi nên tớ ở tạm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.30,0:37:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{Alone?}Một mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.13,0:37:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tớ từng nói mình không có ba mẹ mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.77,0:37:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{This great.}Tuyệt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.94,0:37:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro Mitsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.95,0:37:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry to wait.}Xin lỗi vì để cậu chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.20,0:37:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I read it without permission.}Xin lỗi, tớ đọc mà không xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.95,0:37:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{No problem.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.04,0:37:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro Mitsuo là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.00,0:37:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{My grandfather.}Ông nội tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.50,0:37:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is the manga that Kawasaki-san dropped on the floor yesterday, right?}Manga này hôm bữa Kawasaki ném xuống sàn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.67,0:37:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes, that manga is very precious to me.}Phải, nó là thứ vô giá với tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.92,0:38:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, the paper that emerged from the tunnel is...}Vậy những bản vẽ ở đường hầm...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.26,0:38:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{...a manga your grandfather make?}là manga của ông cậu vẽ?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.76,0:38:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{If that's not,}Nếu không phải,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.26,0:38:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, your manga?}tức là của cậu?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.72,0:38:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.43,0:38:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{I guessed.}Quả nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.10,0:38:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why do you think so?}Tại sao cậu lại nghĩ thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.19,0:38:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{The paper bag over there.}Túi giấy ở bên kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.73,0:38:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{When we first met,}Khi chúng ta lần đầu gặp nhau,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.36,0:38:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're holding that precious bag, right?}cậu đã giữ chặt nó nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.98,0:38:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yutosha is a well-known publisher.}Yutosha là nhà xuất bản nổi tiếng.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.53,0:38:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your grandfather was also a manga artist.}Ông cậu từng là mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.16,0:38:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Plus on your desk full of writing tools,}Trên bàn lại đầy giấy bút vẽ,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.70,0:38:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{obviously I thought so.}nên tớ nghĩ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.62,0:38:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes, that's my manga.}Phải, là manga của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.21,0:38:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{That day, I thought about submitting the manga.}Ngày đó, tớ đã định gửi manga đó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.01,0:38:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why don't you send it?}Sao không gửi?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.76,0:38:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{How many mangaka do you think there are?}Cậu biết ngoài kia có bao nhiêu manga không?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.14,0:38:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe a thousand or more.}Cỡ 1000 hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.35,0:38:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{About five thousand people.}Khoảng 5000 người.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.01,0:38:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Every year, thousands of people wishing to become mangaka send their work.}Mỗi năm, hàng ngàn người đều\N mong muốn trở thành Mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.44,0:38:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{My talent was tested there.}Tớ phải vượt qua số đó bằng tài năng bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.57,0:38:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Pretty scary.}Nó khá đáng sợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.90,0:39:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why I didn't send it.}Thế nên tớ không gửi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.70,0:39:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{But if you don't try, you won't know.}Chưa thử làm sao biết chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:06.45,Top,,0,0,0,,{I know. That's normal.}Tớ biết rất rõ. Bình thường ai chả hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.16,0:39:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{I like the manga my grandfather wrote.}Tớ thích manga ông nội đã vẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.12,0:39:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{But my parents hated my grandfather.}Nhưng ba mẹ tớ ghét ông.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.46,0:39:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{They also hate manga.}Họ cũng ghét manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.00,0:39:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{You know why?}Cậu biết lý do không?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.92,0:39:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.84,0:39:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because the manga didn't sell.}Vì manga đó không bán chạy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.92,0:39:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{That manga was the only series my grandfather ever wrote.}Đó là manga duy nhất ông tớ vẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Only three volumes were published.}Chỉ có 3 tập được xuất bản.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.43,0:39:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, my grandfather kept making manga,}Thế nhưng ông ấy vẫn tiếp tục,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.81,0:39:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even borrowing money from my father.}thậm chí còn mượn tiền từ ba tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.31,0:39:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{When my grandfather died,}Khi ông mất,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.11,0:39:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{My father and mother did not cry.}ba mẹ chẳng ai khóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.15,0:39:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even if they feel relieved.}Thậm chí họ còn cảm thấy nhẹ nhõm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.11,0:39:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{They felt that my grandfather was a burden.}Họ nghĩ ông là mối phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.07,0:39:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{So when I said "I want to be a mangaka",}Thế nên khi tớ nói muốn trở thành mangaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.91,0:39:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{I was immediately kicked out of the house.}ba mẹ đã đuổi tớ ra khỏi nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.66,0:39:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{So that's why you came here?}Và cậu đến đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.54,0:39:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{They want me to come to my senses.}Họ muốn tớ bình tĩnh lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.25,0:39:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{But how can I calm down like this.}Nhưng ai có thể bình thản được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.67,0:40:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is the first manga I made.}Manga đầu tiên tớ vẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.55,0:40:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{The reader is my grandfather.}Người đọc là ông nội.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.17,0:40:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{He said "this is funny".}Ông ấy đã nói "Nó vui đấy".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.09,0:40:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Grandpa also taught me how to love to write manga.}Ông cũng dạy tớ niềm vui vẽ manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.93,0:40:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{But my father found it and threw it away.}Nhưng ba nhìn thấy và vứt hết đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.64,0:40:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{"Do you want to be like your grandfather?", he said.}Ông ấy nói "Mày muốn như ông mày à?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.35,0:40:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{He tore it to pieces...}Và xé nát manga của tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.61,0:40:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{...this manga.}...là nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.11,0:40:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun, do you know about Hanashiro Mitsuo?}Touno nè, cậu biết gì về Hanashiro Mitsuo không?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.69,0:40:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, I don't know.}Xin lỗi, tớ không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.65,0:40:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dĩ nhiên là không.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.82,0:40:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{I once visited several bookstores looking for my grandfather's manga.}Tớ đã tìm manga của ông ở khắp nơi,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.08,0:40:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{But I can't find it.}nhưng không thể tìm thấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.50,0:40:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wherever it is, I do not see my grandfather's manga.}Không nơi nào còn bán nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.67,0:40:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because he's an unknown mangaka.}Vì ông ấy là mangaka không tên tuổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.63,0:40:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why I think...}Thế nên tớ nghĩ...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.21,0:40:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{To leave something in this world...}Để lưu lại gì đó trên thế gian này...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.42,0:40:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{...I must have a special talent.}Tớ phải có tài năng đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.26,0:40:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro, what do you want?}Hanashiro, cậu mong muốn điều gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.85,0:40:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to have a talent to be special.}Tớ muốn trở nên đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.14,0:41:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{That way, I can write a manga that will be remembered in this world forever.}Để tớ có thể tạo nên manga được ghi dấu vào thế giới này.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.61,0:41:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro, Urashima Tunnel is...}Hanashiro, đường hầm Urashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.44,0:41:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.32,0:41:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you saying that such a wish can't be granted?}Cậu định nói điều ước sẽ không thành hiện thực?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.78,0:41:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though you want to return back your sister.}Dù chính cậu cũng muốn mang em gái mình về.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.20,0:41:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.46,0:41:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{The manga you want to publish...}Manga cậu muốn xuất bản...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.92,0:41:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{...can I read it?}...tớ đọc được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.30,0:41:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hah? No!}Hả? Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.63,0:41:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.34,0:41:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm not satisfied with the story, the characters, everything.}Tớ vẫn chưa hài lòng với cốt truyện và nhân vật.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.85,0:41:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why I don't want to publish it.}Thế nên tớ đã không nộp.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.22,0:41:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{But you wrote it so others could read it, right?}Nhưng cậu làm ra nó để ai đọc mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.68,0:41:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even if I'm not satisfied myself.}Ngay cả tớ còn chưa thoả mãn bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.40,0:41:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't let anyone else read it.}Thì không bao giờ để ai đọc cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.15,0:41:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{If no one reads,}Nếu không ai đọc,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.57,0:41:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{A manga is just plain paper.}thì manga chỉ là mớ giấy lộn.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.11,0:41:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Noisy! Looking for trouble, eh?}Phiền phức quá! Cậu muốn đánh nhau à?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.07,0:41:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{This has nothing to do with you, does it?}Vụ này liên quan gì đến cậu?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.74,0:41:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{But we're comrades in arms, right?}Nhưng chúng ta là người cùng chí hướng.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.12,0:42:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{The contents are ordinary.}Nó bình thường lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.00,0:42:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm aware of that.}Tớ biết điều đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.38,0:42:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{I won't know until I read it.}Tớ chưa đọc sao biết được.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.95,0:42:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Interesting.}Thú vị lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.45,0:42:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though the setting is complicated, I can still read it.}Tuy rất phức tạp nhưng tớ có thể đọc hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.79,0:42:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, the arrangement of the plot is right.}Sự sắp xếp cốt truyện rất thú vị.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.17,0:42:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{I was so surprised.}Khúc cuối thật bất ngờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.59,0:42:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can I read it again?}Tớ đọc lại nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.77,0:43:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank You.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.06,0:43:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{I am happy.}Tớ vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.52,0:43:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.31,0:43:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{However, there are 50 thousand people who can make manga of that class.}Nhưng bên ngoài kia có tới\N50.000 người có thể vẽ được nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.48,0:43:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{I know the world is hard.}Tớ biết thế giới này vô cùng khắc nghiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.86,0:43:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why I want to have a special talent.}Đó là lý do tớ muốn có tài năng đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.66,0:43:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{A talent that could leave an imprint on this world.}Tài năng để có thể ghi dấu lên thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.83,0:43:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're great, Hanashiro.}Cậu tuyệt thật, Hanashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.96,0:43:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even now you already have a special talent.}Dù bản thân cậu đã có tài năng.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.92,0:43:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even without going into the tunnel, you're already...}Không cần đi vào đường hầm thì cậu cũng đặc biệt rồi--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.09,0:43:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ngược lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.42,0:43:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Only you are special.}Chỉ có cậu là đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.84,0:43:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{While in the aquarium I realized,}Khi đi thuỷ cung tớ đã nhận ra,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.34,0:43:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{you are like a different person in this world.}cậu không giống với những người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.06,0:43:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{What am I wishing...}Những gì tớ mong muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.27,0:43:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{...was still small and ordinary compared to you.}...so với cậu vẫn chỉ là điều nhỏ bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.02,0:43:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?}Cậu nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.44,0:43:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{You are willing to sacrifice everything without hesitation.}Cậu sẵn sàng hi sinh mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.11,0:43:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just for the sake of making that wish come true.}Chỉ để biến điều ước thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.15,0:43:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why you can find the Urashima Tunnel.}Đó là lý do cậu tìm thấy đường hầm Urashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.49,0:44:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're exaggerating, I just...}Cậu đề cao tớ quá rồi. Tớ chỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.92,0:44:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to go to the world where you are.}Tớ muốn đến thế giới của cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.88,0:44:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why I need the tunnel.}Đó là lý do tớ cần đường hầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.18,0:44:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hei, Touno-kun.}Này, Touno.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.18,0:44:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Tell me the world what you see.}Nói tớ nghe thế giới cậu nhìn thấy như thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.31,0:44:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just a boring world.}Chỉ là một nơi chán ngắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.77,0:44:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not too bad.}Không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.57,0:44:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Next, we go into the tunnel looking for Karen-chan, right?}Tiếp theo chúng ta sẽ tìm Karen-chan nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.37,0:44:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.28,0:44:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{Until then, we're not getting out of that tunnel.}Cho đến lúc đó, chúng ta sẽ không ra khỏi đường hầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.99,0:44:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Me too.}Tớ cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.20,0:44:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm not coming home until I get a special talent.}Tớ sẽ không trở về đến khi có được tài năng.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.46,0:44:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{When?}Khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.13,0:44:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I already decided.}Tớ đã quyết định xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.59,0:44:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{August 2nd.}Ngày 2 tháng 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.30,0:45:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.35,0:45:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{Next week is the summer festival.}Tuần sau là lễ hội mùa hè đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.68,0:45:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sugizaki and I are going there, you want to come?}Sugizaki và tao định đi. Mày sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.35,0:45:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Tao...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.15,0:45:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Want to go with Hanashiro, huh?}Đi với Hanashiro chứ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.86,0:45:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, she already invited you.}Xin lỗi, cậu ấy mời mày trước nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.07,0:45:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro said that...}Hanashiro với tao...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.57,0:45:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's not bad either.}Cũng không tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.13,0:45:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Am I late?}Tớ đến trễ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.55,0:45:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, you came early.}Không, cậu đến sớm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.43,0:45:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's not time to assemble yet.}Vẫn chưa đến giờ hẹn.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.56,0:45:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have to come 10 minutes before the meet up time.}Tớ luôn đến sớm 10 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.64,0:45:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're serious too, huh.}Cậu nghiêm túc ghê nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.86,0:45:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's go.}Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.90,0:46:39.07,Italics,,0,0,0,,{After this, the fireworks show will start.}Pháo hoa chuẩn bị bắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.61,0:46:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{It says "no entry" here, right?}Chỗ này ghi cấm vào đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.37,0:46:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{In the past, this was me and my sister's secret place.}Hồi xưa từng là chỗ bí mật của hai anh em tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.17,0:46:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why did you bring me here?}Sao lại dẫn tớ đến đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.63,0:47:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't know when I can come back.}Tớ không biết có thể quay lại không.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.93,0:47:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe I won't be able to come back after a thousand years.}Có thể sẽ mất cả ngàn năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.47,0:47:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{At the time...}Lúc đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.51,0:47:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{It'll be Touno-kun, Karen-chan and me, right?}Sẽ là tớ, Touno và Karen nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.98,0:47:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{At that time, are manga still existed?}Lúc đó vẫn còn manga chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.06,0:47:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{A pictures and stories already exist since thousands of years ago.}Ảnh và những câu chuyện sẽ còn mãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.28,0:47:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{Manga that tells with pictures will definitely not disappear.}Manga là những bức ảnh nên sẽ không biến mất đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.40,0:47:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, I think it's good.}Vậy thì chắc sẽ ổn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.73,0:47:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{May I ask why you chose August 2nd?}Mà sao cậu lại chọn ngày 2 tháng 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.36,0:48:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{When me and Karen got here,}Khi Karen và tớ đến đây,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.50,0:48:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{my parents had a big fight at home.}ba mẹ đã cãi nhau rất lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.61,0:48:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{The two of us came here like running away from home.}Nên bọn tớ trốn khỏi nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.37,0:48:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Karen was very agitated.}Karen rất cứng rắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.25,0:48:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{She cries.}Nhưng con bé đã khóc.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.25,0:48:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{And August 2nd was the day she died.}Và ngày 8 tháng 2 cũng là ngày giỗ con bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.27,0:49:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, I give up.}Ôi chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.98,0:49:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{This sushi is expensive, right?}Món sushi này mắc lắm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.57,0:49:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.82,0:49:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{Duh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.20,0:49:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{But I'm happy.}Nhưng em vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.99,0:49:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ya, ya.}Ừ ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.99,0:49:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Come on, eat up.}Nào nào, ăn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.71,0:49:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Who's that?}Ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.75,0:49:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're home, huh.}Con về rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.38,0:49:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look, here we are.}Nào, là nó đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.09,0:49:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is my son, Kaoru.}Con trai anh, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.39,0:49:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah, so it's you...}A, là cháu...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.85,0:49:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Pleased to meet you.}Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.39,0:50:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Come on, greets her too.}Nào, chào hỏi đi chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.06,0:50:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{She will be your new mother.}Cô ấy sẽ là mẹ mới của con.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.91,0:50:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{What does it mean?}Vậy là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.07,0:50:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll tell you sometime.}Ba định nói từ trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.11,0:50:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{But well, my job is getting harder,}Nhưng mà... do công việc bận rộn.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.70,0:50:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{so it's hard to find the right time.}Nên chưa tìm được thời điểm thích hợp.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.03,0:50:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{Although a bit rushed, but not too slow...}Xin lỗi vì không nói sớm, nhưng mà chuyện là vậy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.45,0:50:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look, now is a little celebration.}Giờ ba đang ăn mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.00,0:50:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nào, uống thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.91,0:50:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your physical examination results are bad, right?}Kết quả kiểm tra sức khoẻ của anh không tốt mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.46,0:50:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{But today is special, anyway.}Nhưng hôm nay là ngày đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.25,0:50:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Kaoru, we also have a moving plan.}Kaoru, ba cũng đã lên kế hoạch chuyển nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.59,0:50:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm planning to move to Tokyo.}Chúng ta sẽ chuyển đến Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.63,0:50:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{And also plans to change jobs.}Và ba cũng chuyển việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.39,0:50:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hope you get the decision, ok?}Quyết định mau chóng đúng là tuyệt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.22,0:50:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{We will start a new life now.}Chúng ta sẽ bắt đầu cuộc sống mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.27,0:50:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's up, Kaoru?}Sao thế Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.94,0:50:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why are you crying?}Sao con khóc?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.32,0:50:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{You!}Mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.57,0:50:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?}Mày làm trò gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.25,0:51:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey, where are you go, Kaoru?}Này, con đi đâu vậy Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.84,0:51:17.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,{I can hear frogs...}Tôi có thể nghe tiếng ếch ộp...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.39,0:51:21.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,{...from afar.}từ phía xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.85,0:51:26.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,{I can hear frogs...}Tôi có thể nghe tiếng ếch ộp...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.40,0:51:31.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,{...from afar.}Từ phía xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.48,0:52:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{The atmosphere is good, isn't it?}Chỗ này tuyệt nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.73,0:52:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Quán này lâu lắm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.48,0:52:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{I used to come here when I was little with my family.}Tớ thường hay đến cùng gia đình.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.36,0:52:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can we play games on this table?}Chúng ta có thể chơi game trên bàn này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.03,0:52:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can, but once play is 100 yen.}Được chứ. Một lần 100 yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.20,0:52:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll try sometime.}Lần tới tớ sẽ thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.58,0:52:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is going on today?}Hôm nay có chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.96,0:52:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Recently, yy manga that I lend to you.}Đợt trước cậu đã đọc manga của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.47,0:52:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{After that, I sending it to Yutosha.}Sau đó, tớ đã gửi nó đến Yutosha.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.72,0:52:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though it's hard to write, I don't expect more.}Thực tình tớ không hi vọng gì nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.64,0:52:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't even want to hope for anything.}Cũng chẳng mong chờ gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.23,0:52:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.15,0:52:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{This morning, I got a call from the magazine editor.}Sáng nay, bên nhà xuất bản đã gọi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.65,0:52:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{They seem to like my manga.}Có vẻ họ thích manga của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.61,0:53:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{They offered me to make manga together.}Họ muốn tớ cùng làm manga với họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.66,0:53:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{So you debuted as a mangaka?}Vậy là cậu sẽ ra mắt như một mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.29,0:53:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, this is just the editor's personal decision.}Không, chỉ là quyết định cá nhân của biên tập viên.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.75,0:53:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{The rest, stil not decided yet.}Vẫn chưa quyết định gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.42,0:53:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't really understand manga.}Tớ thực sự không hiểu manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.84,0:53:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{That means someone needs you, right?}Nhưng tức là có ai đó đã tìm thấy cậu rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.01,0:53:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{It could be...}Có thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.72,0:53:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe not a big thing.}Nhưng cũng chẳng có gì to tát.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.85,0:53:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe they just need me right now.}Nhiều khi họ chỉ cần tớ lúc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.35,0:53:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{It was because of his personal decision.}Là vì quyết định của biên tập viên đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.94,0:53:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.23,0:53:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry to wait.}Xin lỗi vì đã chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.19,0:53:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is a mixed sandwich.}Đây là sandwich đầy đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.36,0:53:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{And here is the omelette rice.}Và đây là cơm omelette.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.24,0:53:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{Please enjoy.}Xin hãy tận hưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.79,0:53:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's the point.}Chỉ thế thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.75,0:53:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just to let you know.}Tớ muốn cho cậu biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.79,0:53:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{The important thing is, tomorrow we go into the tunnel, right?}Quan trọng là ngày mai chúng ta sẽ vào đường hầm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.92,0:54:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you ready?}Cậu sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.93,0:54:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can we hold off for a bit?}Liệu có thể lùi lại chút không?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.35,0:54:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.52,0:54:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{We have to think again carefully.}Tớ nghĩ cần phải suy nghĩ cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.36,0:54:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've thought about it.}Tớ cũng đã nghĩ kĩ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.40,0:54:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{I've been thinking about getting into that tunnel.}Và đã chọn đi vào đường hầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.44,0:54:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{In that case, I don't need to tell you, right?}Nếu vậy thì tớ không cần phải nói điều gì nữa nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.28,0:54:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun, I don't like the way you talk.}Touno, tớ không thích cách nói đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.57,0:54:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but this is an important matter.}Xin lỗi, nhưng đây là chuyện quan trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.45,0:54:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're actually still not sure, right?}Cậu vẫn còn đang do dự nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.79,0:54:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Tớ...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.08,0:54:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{I... can't go on like this.}Tớ... không thể cứ thế này mãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.59,0:54:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't have confidence.}Tớ không có tự tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.68,0:54:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why I have to be a special person.}Thế nên phải trở thành người đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.69,0:54:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.81,0:54:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't even know what to do.}Tớ chẳng biết mình phải làm gì nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.58,0:55:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{For now, let's eat.}Tạm thời cứ ăn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.75,0:55:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{I can't think on an empty stomach.}Đói sẽ không suy nghĩ được gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.69,0:55:44.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Currently, the Kawagata to Oosara trains,}Hiện tại, tàu từ Kawagata đến Oosara,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.03,0:55:46.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,{had an accidents due to animal collisions.}đang gặp tai nạn với thú hoang.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.57,0:55:53.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Due to that, the next train will come about 30 minutes later.}Chuyến tiếp theo sẽ trễ 30 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.25,0:55:56.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,{We apologize for the inconvenience.}Chúng tôi rất xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.04,0:55:58.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Please wait a moment.}Xin hãy chờ ít phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.27,0:56:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{You don't look like you're used to being here.}Có vẻ cậu không phải người ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.78,0:56:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{The train is late because of the deer, it's common here.}Khu này tàu hay đi trễ vì tai nạn tông trúng hươu lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.58,0:56:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is my my umbrella. Want to use?}Dù của tớ đây, muốn dùng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.00,0:56:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{You are just there.}Chẳng hợp chút nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.59,0:56:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{What do you want to do?}Cậu định làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.80,0:56:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because you don't have an umbrella,}Thấy cậu không có dù.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.80,0:56:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{If your clothes are wet, it will be troublesome.}Nếu quần áo ướt sẽ phiền phức lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.81,0:56:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Guess what? Want to look good?}Nói gì thế? Muốn ra vẻ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.60,0:56:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{If I borrow it, then what will you use?}Nếu mượn rồi thì cậu dùng gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.27,0:57:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's okay because my house is near from the station.}Không sao, nhà tớ gần ga mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.65,0:57:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's not an answer.}Chẳng ăn khớp chút nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.44,0:57:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aren't your parents worried if you get sick?}Ba mẹ cậu sẽ lo khi cậu bệnh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.07,0:57:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{My parents kicked me out.}Ba mẹ tớ đá ra khỏi nhà rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.82,0:57:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well then, great,}Tuyệt thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.28,0:57:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{In my house there is only an annoying father.}Nhà tớ chỉ có mỗi ông già phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.58,0:57:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can I borrow your umbrella?}Tớ có thể mượn cây dù chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.54,0:57:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.58,0:57:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Can you tell me your name and phone number.}Tên cậu và số điện thoại là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.38,0:57:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Touno Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.72,0:57:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.36,0:57:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not bad, your smiling face.}Không tệ, khuôn mặt lúc cười của cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.82,0:57:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{You too.}Cả cậu nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.99,0:57:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.99,0:57:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have to return your umbrella.}Tớ phải trả lại dù cho cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.08,0:57:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Because I was busy, I forgot.}Bận rộn quá nên quên luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.04,0:57:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's okay to throw it away.}Thôi, vứt đi được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.41,0:57:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{That just a cheap umbrella.}Chỉ là cây dù rẻ tiền mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.75,0:58:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{I must return what I borrowed.}Tớ phải trả lại đồ đã mượn.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.46,0:58:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cũng chẳng có gì to tát mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.50,0:58:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.14,0:58:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bạn của Kaoru à?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.10,0:58:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.14,0:58:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{He ran away from home and never came back.}Nó đi ra khỏi nhà từ tối qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.22,0:59:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't know where he went, but it was a habit like this.}Bác cũng chẳng biết nó đi đâu nữa\Nnhưng lúc nào cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.14,0:59:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{So, don't worry too much...}Nên cháu đừng lo lắng gì cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.46,0:59:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun!}Touno!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.88,0:59:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun!}Touno!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.80,0:59:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun!}Touno!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.97,0:59:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun!}Touno!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.93,0:59:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun!}Touno!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.85,0:59:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun!}Touno!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.94,0:59:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?!}Tại sao?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.38,1:00:14.01,Italics,,0,0,0,,{When this message is received,}Khi tin nhắn này đến được cậu,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.01,1:00:17.76,Italics,,0,0,0,,{that means I've stepped into the Urashima Tunnel.}cũng là lúc tớ đã bước vào đường hầm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.47,1:00:20.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Maybe you're angry,}Có thể cậu sẽ giận lắm,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.68,1:00:22.14,Italics,,0,0,0,,{or maybe disappointed,}hoặc thất vọng,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.77,1:00:24.56,Italics,,0,0,0,,{or maybe both.}hoặc cả hai.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.18,1:00:25.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,{But,}Nhưng,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.89,1:00:30.11,Italics,,0,0,0,,{You are not a person who can enter the Urashima Tunnel.}cậu không phải là người nên vào đây.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.40,1:00:34.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,{You said you wanted to have a special talent,}Cậu từng nói muốn có tài năng đặc biệt,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.74,1:00:36.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,{But I think you already have that talent.}nhưng tớ nghĩ cậu đã có nó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.99,1:00:39.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,{I really enjoy your manga,}Tớ rất thích manga của cậu,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.24,1:00:42.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,{even get offers from editors.}và cả biên tập viên đó.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.58,1:00:45.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Since then you've been special.}Chứng tỏ cậu đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.46,1:00:48.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,{I want to read your manga,}Tớ muốn đọc manga của cậu.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.13,1:00:51.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,{and more manga, shorts and serials.}Thật nhiều tập, truyện ngắn lẫn truyện dài.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.55,1:00:54.09,Italics,,0,0,0,,{So, I want you to continue writing manga,}Vậy nên hãy tiếp tục vẽ nó,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.47,1:00:59.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,{And I want to tell you what I know about the Urashima Tunnel.}và tớ sẽ nói cho cậu nghe những gì \Nmình biết về đường hầm Urashima.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.35,1:01:03.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,{"A tunnel where you can ask anything".}"Đường hầm biến mọi thứ thành hiện thực".
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.89,1:01:05.93,Italics,,0,0,0,,{I guess that's wrong.}Tớ nghĩ không phải.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.77,1:01:08.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,{The Urashima Tunnel...}Đường hầm Urashima...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.96,1:01:33.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,{The Urashima Tunnel is a tunnel that can restore what is lost.}Là nơi lấy lại những gì đã mất.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.17,1:01:38.76,Italics,,0,0,0,,{So, even if you go in, you don't get that talent.}Thế nên dù có vào thì cũng sẽ không thể có tài năng.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.30,1:01:42.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,{So I have to enter this tunnel alone.}Vậy nên tớ sẽ đi một mình.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.26,1:01:47.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Hanashiro, you should write manga.}Hanashiro, cậu nên trở thành mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.43,1:01:50.73,Italics,,0,0,0,,{You have to leave a trace that you live in your world.}Hãy để lại dấu tích của mình ở thế giới này.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.40,1:01:55.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,{If I appeared a thousand years later,}Nếu 1000 năm sau tớ quay lại,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.40,1:01:57.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,{at that time I wanted to read your manga.}lúc đó tớ sẽ đọc manga của cậu.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.20,1:02:02.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Our cooperation last month was very pleasant.}Một tháng qua đã rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.78,1:02:04.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,{So now...}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.06,1:02:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{What the hell was that?}Cái quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.69,1:02:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{Cheat!}Ăn gian!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.86,1:02:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Coward!}Hèn nhát!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.98,1:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just looking at yourself!}Chỉ toàn nghĩ đến bản thân!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.57,1:02:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though you don't understand me at all!}Chẳng hiểu gì về tớ cả!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.53,1:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{So all this time you were just pretending?}Trước giờ cậu chỉ ra vẻ thôi à?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.11,1:02:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Go alone without saying anything!}Đi một mình và chẳng thèm nói gì!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.87,1:02:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúng ta là người chung chí hướng mà!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.41,1:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Don't decide on your own!}Đừng có tự quyết định chứ!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.00,1:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Những cảm xúc...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.80,1:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{With what feelings do I...}Những cảm xúc của tớ...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.39,1:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{I just want to be with you.}Em chỉ muốn được bên cạnh anh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.06,1:03:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even sacrificing everything in this world.}Dù có phải vứt bỏ cả thế giới này.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.33,1:03:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{14 hours and a half here, it's been 4 years outside.}14 tiếng rưỡi, hơn 4 năm rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.55,1:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{Karen...}Karen...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.23,1:03:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.41,1:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where?}Em ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.37,1:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.41,1:04:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where?}Ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.03,1:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Uh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.83,1:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, you awake.}Anh dậy rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.45,1:04:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.54,1:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmm? What?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.25,1:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is that banana juice?}Là nước ép chuối à?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.25,1:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes. Want to have a drink together?}Đúng rồi, uống cùng nhau nhé?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.51,1:05:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{I think I had a strange dream just now.}Anh vừa mơ giấc mơ kì lạ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.01,1:05:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lạ như nào?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.85,1:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{I forget.}Anh quên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.93,1:05:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{Forget, huh?}Quên à?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.23,1:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{I still remember my dream, you know.}Em vẫn nhớ giấc mơ của mình đó.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.65,1:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Recently, I had a dream of catching 100 Hercules beetles with Onii-chan.}Gần đây em mơ bắt 100 con bọ cánh cứng với anh.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.07,1:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{Uh, really!}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.74,1:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.36,1:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wait a minute.}Chờ em chút.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.83,1:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look!}Nhìn nè!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.46,1:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rhinoceros beetle!}Bọ cánh cứng!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.75,1:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{I caught it for you.}Em bắt nó cho anh đó.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.09,1:05:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wow.}Tuyệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.30,1:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's big, right?}To phải không?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.51,1:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where did you get it from?}Em bắt nó ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.88,1:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Secret.}Bí mật.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.80,1:05:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{What. Tell me.}Nói anh nghe đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.84,1:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{If I tell you, you'll look for it later, right?}Nếu em nói thì anh lại bỏ đi bắt nó chứ gì?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.68,1:05:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{You know huh.}Lộ rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.47,1:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{Of course!}Chứ gì nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.52,1:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah, I'll make dinner, 'kay.}A, em sẽ làm bữa tối.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.69,1:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{You?}Em á?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.56,1:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes, I'm the one who cooks.}Vâng, em biết nấu ăn mà.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.52,1:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{What are you going to cook?}Em định nấu gì?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.15,1:06:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is it...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.73,1:06:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{Cup udon...}Mì ly...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.90,1:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Or onigiri, which is heated in the microwave.}Cơm nắm xong bỏ lò vi sóng.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.61,1:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is that really you who cooks it?}Cái đó mà gọi là tự nấu hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.20,1:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{Obviously.}Chứ gì nữa!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.91,1:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{After all, I'm the one who poured the hot water...}Vì em bỏ nước vào, vo gạo...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.91,1:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{...also heated the onigiri in the microwave...}...và bỏ cơm nắm vào lò vi sóng...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.00,1:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{...And I also put it on the plate.}Rồi bày ra dĩa nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.13,1:06:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{That make me the one who cook it...}Thế nên em là người nấu.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.34,1:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ouch, it's spilled!}Đổ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.67,1:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll get a lap.}Em đi lấy khăn.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.05,1:06:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{Where is this?}Đây là đâu?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.16,1:07:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm not losing this,}Mình không bị lấy mất...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.70,1:07:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{But I threw it away.}Mà đã vứt bỏ nó.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.51,1:07:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.99,1:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{The message should not have been sent.}Đáng ra tin nhắn phải không nhận được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.45,1:07:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.33,1:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is that your friend, Onii-chan?}Bạn của anh hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.00,1:07:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, not my friend anymore.}Không, không còn là bạn anh nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.04,1:07:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Are you guys arguing?}Hai người cãi nhau hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.30,1:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's not the case.}Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.59,1:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{Fighting with friends is not good, you know.}Cãi nhau với bạn bè không tốt đâu.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.97,1:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Besides, Onii-chan doesn't have much friends.}Với cả anh cũng ít bạn bè nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.51,1:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's okay, as long as you're still there.}Không sao, miễn là có em.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.22,1:08:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{I know.}Em biết.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.21,1:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{You really likes me.}Anh thực sự thích em nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.56,1:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's why I always laugh when in front of you.}Thế nên em sẽ luôn cười trước mặt anh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.81,1:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{'cause I also really like you.}Vì em cũng yêu quý anh mà.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.15,1:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{I am also like that.}Anh cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.86,1:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{But I want you to liked by other people too.}Nhưng em muốn anh cũng yêu quý những người khác nữa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.79,1:08:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Anh...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.75,1:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{And then...}Và sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.21,1:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{If the person you likes, likes you back...}Nếu người đó thích anh và anh cũng thế...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.88,1:08:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{Then we all can laugh together!}Thì tất cả chúng ta có thể cười đùa cùng nhau!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.78,1:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.90,1:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to be beside Karen.}Mình muốn bên cạnh Karen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.58,1:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{But now...}Nhưng bây giờ...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.37,1:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's someone I want to meet!}Có người anh cần phải gặp lại!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.00,1:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{I know.}Em biết.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.64,1:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{Onii-chan, I love you!}Em thích anh, anh à.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.81,1:09:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Be careful!}Anh đi cẩn thận.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.36,1:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'll leave!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.54,1:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sensei, because there is the last train, I'll go home first, okay.}Sensei, chuyến tàu cuối rồi nên em về trước nhé?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.00,1:09:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank You.}À ừ.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.04,1:09:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Tomorrow I'll come at 10 am.}Ngày mai em sẽ đến lúc 10 giờ sáng.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.00,1:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes please.}Ừ, em vất vả rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.46,1:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Alright, thanks for your hardwork.}Vậy em xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.32,1:10:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{You won't take the umbrella from me?}Anh không định để em trả lại cây dù à?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.67,1:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.85,1:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.82,1:10:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.11,1:11:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.41,1:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.79,1:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Anh...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.05,1:11:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{I have something I want to tell you.}Có chuyện cần nói với em!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.74,1:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{You better just rest first.}Em nên nghỉ ngơi chút đi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.08,1:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Since your debut, you have continued to serialize.}Từ ngày ra mắt em đã luôn làm việc không nghỉ.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.67,1:11:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can still write, really.}Em sẽ có thể vẽ lại sớm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.05,1:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry.}Em xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.84,1:12:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{You always carry that umbrella,}Lúc nào em cũng mang theo chiếc dù đó.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.56,1:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{is that some kind of amulet?}Là bùa hộ mệnh hả?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.48,1:12:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{This...}Nó...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.57,1:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{For now, I'll figure out a way to serialize it.}Thôi, anh sẽ tìm cách sắp xếp cho.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.90,1:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{So don't worry.}Em đừng lo gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.82,1:12:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{For now, the important thing is that you rest.}Quan trọng bây giờ là nghỉ ngơi tịnh dưỡng.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.66,1:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.67,1:12:46.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Currently, the Oosara to Sugimori trains,}Tàu từ Sugimori đến Oosara,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.80,1:12:49.39,Italics,,0,0,0,,{had an accidents due to animal collisions.}đã gặp tai nạn với thú hoang.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.47,1:12:56.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Due to that, the next train will come about 30 minutes later.}Chuyến tiếp theo sẽ trễ 30 phút.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.94,1:12:58.94,Italics,,0,0,0,,{We apologize for the inconvenience.}Chúng tôi vô cùng xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.48,1:13:00.69,Italics,,0,0,0,,{Please wait a moment.}Xin hãy chờ trong ít phút.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.97,1:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{I...}Em...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.72,1:13:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{...always thinking of you Touno-kun...}...lúc nào cũng nghĩ về anh...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.01,1:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{..always...}luôn luôn...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.29,1:15:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun.}Touno.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.54,1:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun.}Touno.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.00,1:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{Touno-kun.}Touno nè.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.38,1:15:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hana...shiro?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.14,1:15:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.68,1:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's been 8 years.}Đã 8 năm rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.22,1:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why are you here?}Tại sao lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.64,1:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{You were slow, so I picked you up.}Anh chậm quá nên em đến đón.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.11,1:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though we've say goodbye.}Dù chúng ta đã nói tạm biệt.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.23,1:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{Our plan is still not finished, right?}Nhưng kế hoạch vẫn chưa kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.49,1:15:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{I want to send you a message...}Anh đã muốn gửi em tin nhắn...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.12,1:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{And surprised you.}Và bị té...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.25,1:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Already received.}Em nhận được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.50,1:16:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well received.}Nhận được rõ ràng luôn.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.59,1:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sorry to make you waiting.}Xin lỗi vì đã để em chờ.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.86,1:16:35.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,{The kiss lasted only 10 seconds, but outside it was 6 and a half hours.}Nụ hôn chỉ 10 giây nhưng bên ngoài đã mất tận 6 tiếng rưỡi.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.71,1:16:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's been 13 years old...}Đã 13 năm trôi qua...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.09,1:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{...and 102 days.}và 102 ngày...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.30,1:17:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{A lot has changed, huh.}Nhiều thứ đã thay đổi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.47,1:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{Not all of them, really.}Không phải đâu.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.56,1:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's not even a thousand years.}Vẫn chưa đủ 1000 năm mà.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.06,1:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Đúng là thế.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.98,1:17:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{I might be able to read your publications.}Anh muốn đọc thử truyện của em.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.52,1:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{How do you know?}Sao anh biết.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.19,1:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{I received the message.}Anh nhận được tin nhắn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.11,1:17:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{Even though I shouldn't be able to receive it when you send from outside.}Dù đáng ra là không thể nhận được tin nhắn từ bên ngoài.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.95,1:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Maybe we're taken back...}Có lẽ chúng ta đã lấy lại được...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.41,1:17:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{...by the Urashima Tunnel.}...nhờ đường hầm Urashima.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.76,1:17:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Rain?}Mưa?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.68,1:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{The umbrella!}Dù!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.82,1:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{You always carry it?}Em luôn mang theo nó à?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.44,1:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{Finally I can return it.}Cuối cùng em đã có thể trả lại.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.07,1:17:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{This way, we don't owe each other anymore.}Từ giờ hai ta hết nợ nần gì nhé.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.57,1:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's been 13 years tho.}13 năm rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.45,1:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.29,1:18:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{Let's think about it from now on.}Từ giờ hãy cùng nhau nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.04,1:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{From now on, huh?}Từ giờ à?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.38,1:18:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanashiro.
